description: Returns the definition of a specific DataBrew schedule.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The name of the schedule to be described.

nested_items.name: CreateDate
nested_items.description: The date and time that the schedule was created.

nested_items.name: CreatedBy
nested_items.description: The identifier (user name) of the user who created the schedule.

nested_items.name: JobNames
nested_items.description: The name or names of one or more jobs to be run by using the schedule.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedBy
nested_items.description: The identifier (user name) of the user who last modified the schedule.

nested_items.name: LastModifiedDate
nested_items.description: The date and time that the schedule was last modified.

nested_items.name: ResourceArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the schedule.

nested_items.name: CronExpression
nested_items.description: The date or dates and time or times when the jobs are to be run for the schedule. For more information, see Cron expressions in the Glue DataBrew Developer Guide.
